xt_8g9Y3x":{"type":"richtext","settings":{"text":"<p>Profitez des bienfaits du <strong>caf\u00e9 vert d\u00e9caf\u00e9in\u00e9</strong> combin\u00e9 au <strong>gingembre</strong>.</p>","position":"top_left"}},"richtext_NFTkBh":{"type":"richtext","settings":{"text":"<p>Ce duo, naturellement riche en acide chlorog\u00e9nique et en L-carnitine, soutient l\u2019organisme dans sa capacit\u00e9 \u00e0 utiliser davantage de graisses comme source d\u2019\u00e9nergie. </p><p>Peut augmenter la d\u00e9pense calorique d\u2019environ <strong>10 % sur plusieurs heures</strong>, sans caf\u00e9ine et sans effet de chute d\u2019\u00e9nergie.Une saveur douce, ronde, avec une <strong>note de noisette vanill\u00e9e</strong>.</p>","position":"bottom_left"}},"button_47CABF":{"type":"button","settings":{"text":"je commande","url":"shopify://collections/all","position":"bottom_left","style":"solid","background":"#7d3fff","text_color":"#ffffff"}}},"block_order":["subheading_Ec4aUM","heading_xWBtGT","richtext_8g9Y3x","richtext_NFTkBh","button_47CABF"],"name":"t:sections.text_with_media.name","settings":{"color_scheme":"","content_position":"start","content_percentage_width":50,"overlay_color":"#000000","overlay_opacity":20,"add_media_spacing":false,"autoplay_video":false,"primary_image":"shopify://shop_images/FOND_FIN.jpg","secondary_media_width":55,"secondary_media_mobile_width":60,"show_secondary_media_on_mobile":true,"secondary_media_alignment":"place-self-center","secondary_media_shape":"none"}},"text_with_media_HYdW4P":{"type":"text-with-media","blocks":{"subheading_AzRfPX":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"text":"valeurs","position":"top_left"}},"heading_T6yRr8":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"Effet coupe-faim. R\u00e9sultats v\u00e9rifi\u00e9s en laboratoire.","heading_tag":"h3","position":"top_left","highlight_effect":"default","highlight_accent_color":"","highlight_text_color":""}},"richtext_EqtyF9":{"type":"richtext","settings":{"text":"<p>UBURN commence \u00e0 agir d\u00e8s la premi\u00e8re prise gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 plus de <strong>9 ingr\u00e9dients naturels</strong> sp\u00e9cialement pens\u00e9s pour les femmes qui veulent enfin <strong>arr\u00eater de grignoter et reprendre le contr\u00f4le</strong>.</p>","position":"top_left"}},"richtext_JL8jd6":{"type":"richtext","settings":{"text":"<p>Dans une dose, tu retrouves :</p><ul><li><strong>L\u2019ube violet</strong>, une racine des Philippines ultra-riche en fibres qui aide vraiment \u00e0 tenir entre les repas.<br/></li><li><strong>Le konjac</strong>, une fibre capable d\u2019absorber jusqu\u2019\u00e0 100\u00d7 son poids en eau.<br/></li></ul><p>Une fois dans ton estomac, les deux forment un <strong>gel naturel qui remplit bien</strong> et calme les envies de manger.</p>","position":"bottom_left"}},"button_PTPMEK":{"type":"button","settings":{"text":"Voir nos ingr\u00e9dients","url":"shopify://pages/ingredients","position":"bottom_left","style":"solid","background":"#7d3fff","text_color":"#ffffff"}}},"block_order":["subheading_AzRfPX","heading_T6yRr8","richtext_EqtyF9","richtext_JL8jd6","button_PTPMEK"],"name":"t:sections.text_with_media.name","settings":{"color_scheme":"","content_position":"end","content_percentage_width":50,"overlay_color":"#000000","overlay_opacity":20,"add_media_spacing":false,"autoplay_video":false,"primary_image":"shopify://shop_images/Powder.jpg","secondary_media_width":55,"secondary_media_mobile_width":60,"show_secondary_media_on_mobile":true,"secondary_media_alignment":"place-self-center","secondary_media_shape":"none"}},"separator_adjustable_Fi6xnq":{"type":"separator-adjustable","name":"S\u00e9parateur r\u00e9glable","settings":{"color":"#dad4e2","thickness":1,"width":100,"line_style":"solid","spacing_top":0,"spacing_bottom":0}},"1763466816ac9eee2b":{"type":"apps","blocks":{"loox_reviews_loox_dynamic_section_kaEhEh":{"type":"shopify://apps/loox-reviews/blocks/loox-dynamic-section/5c3b337f-fd14-4df5-b1d6-80ec13e6e28e","settings":{"reviews_to_display":"","default_tab":"automatic","only_photos":false,"aggregated":false,"limit":20,"hide_thumbnails":false,"maxwidth":1080,"is_sample":false}},"section-header":{"type":"_section-header","static":true,"settings":{"subheading":"","title":"T\u00e9moignages","content":"<p>D\u00e9couvrez les avis de celles et ceux qui ont fait d\u2019<strong>Uburn</strong> un essentiel de leur routine.</p>","button_text":"","button_link":"","button_style":"outline","text_alignment":"left","heading_size":"h3","title_icon":"none","show_scrolling_title":false},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["loox_reviews_loox_dynamic_section_kaEhEh"],"settings":{"color_scheme":"","add_vertical_spacing":true,"add_horizontal_spacing":true}},"collection_list_r8VBKW":{"type":"collection-list","blocks":{"section-header":{"type":"_section-header","static":true,"settings":{"subheading":"","title":"\u00e9tapes","content":"<p>Pr\u00e9levez simplement <strong>une dose d\u2019UBE</strong> gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 la cuill\u00e8re doseuse fournie, la quantit\u00e9 id\u00e9ale pour un <strong>apport pr\u00e9cis et imm\u00e9diat</strong>. Versez ensuite cette dose dans une gourde remplie de <strong>250 ml d\u2019eau, de lait ou m\u00eame de caf\u00e9</strong>, selon vos pr\u00e9f\u00e9rences. <strong>Secouez soigneusement</strong>, puis savourez une <strong>boisson gourmande, pratique et efficace</strong>, \u00e0 d\u00e9guster o\u00f9 vous voulez et quand vous le souhaitez.</p><p><a href=\"/products/ube-poudre\" title=\"UBE - POUDRE\"><strong>Passez \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9tape sup\u00e9rieure et commandez.</strong></a></p>","button_text":"","button_link":"","button_style":"outline","text_alignment":"left","heading_size":"h3","title_icon":"none","show_scrolling_title":false},"blocks":{}}},"name":"t:sections.collection_list.name","settings":{"color_scheme":"","items_per_row":3,"stack_on_mobile":true,"add_horizontal_spacing":true,"content_position":"inside","column_spacing":"md","image_size":"auto"}},"faq_ahgahg":{"type":"faq","blocks":{"category_securite":{"type":"category","settings":{"title":"S\u00e9curit\u00e9 et Composition","icon":"picto-ingredient","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"question_allergenes":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"UBurn contient-il des allerg\u00e8nes ou substances nocives ?","answer":"<p>Non, UBurn ne contient pas d'allerg\u00e8nes courants. Tous nos ingr\u00e9dients sont d'origine naturelle et soigneusement s\u00e9lectionn\u00e9s pour leur s\u00e9curit\u00e9 et leur efficacit\u00e9. Notre formule est certifi\u00e9e sans gluten, sans lactose et sans OGM.</p>","icon":"none","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"question_danger_sante":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"Est-ce que UBurn est sans danger pour la sant\u00e9 ?","answer":"<p>Oui, UBurn est sans danger pour la sant\u00e9 lorsqu'il est consomm\u00e9 conform\u00e9ment aux recommandations. Notre formule est d\u00e9velopp\u00e9e avec des ingr\u00e9dients naturels et valid\u00e9e par des experts en nutrition. Toutefois, en cas de doute, consultez votre m\u00e9decin avant de commencer.</p>","icon":"none","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"category_efficacite":{"type":"category","settings":{"title":"Efficacit\u00e9 et R\u00e9sultats","icon":"picto-star","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"question_perte_poids":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"Comment UBurn agit-il sur la perte de poids ?","answer":"<p>UBurn agit sur plusieurs leviers : il booste le m\u00e9tabolisme, r\u00e9duit l'app\u00e9tit et favorise la combustion des graisses. Gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 ses actifs naturels, il aide votre corps \u00e0 transformer les graisses en \u00e9nergie plus efficacement.</p>","icon":"none","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"question_combien_temps":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"Combien de temps avant de voir des r\u00e9sultats ?","answer":"<p>La plupart des utilisateurs remarquent une r\u00e9duction de l'app\u00e9tit d\u00e8s la premi\u00e8re semaine. Les r\u00e9sultats visibles sur le poids apparaissent g\u00e9n\u00e9ralement apr\u00e8s 2 \u00e0 4 semaines d'utilisation r\u00e9guli\u00e8re, associ\u00e9e \u00e0 une alimentation \u00e9quilibr\u00e9e.</p>","icon":"none","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"category_utilisation":{"type":"category","settings":{"title":"Utilisation et Pr\u00e9paration","icon":"picto-recipe","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"question_quand_prendre":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"Quand prendre UBurn et combien de fois par jour ?","answer":"<p>Nous recommandons de prendre UBurn 1 \u00e0 3 fois par jour selon votre objectif, de pr\u00e9f\u00e9rence le matin ou avant les repas. Chaque dose se pr\u00e9pare en m\u00e9langeant 1 mesure de poudre avec 250 ml d'eau froide ou chaude.</p>","icon":"none","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"question_comment_preparer":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"Comment pr\u00e9parer UBurn ?","answer":"<p>M\u00e9langez simplement 1 mesure (10g) de poudre UBurn avec 250 ml d'eau. Vous pouvez le consommer chaud ou froid selon vos pr\u00e9f\u00e9rences. Vous pouvez aussi l'incorporer dans un smoothie ou un yaourt.</p>","icon":"none","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"category_contre_indications":{"type":"category","settings":{"title":"Contre-indications et Pr\u00e9cautions","icon":"picto-document","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"question_contre_indications":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"Y a-t-il des contre-indications \u00e0 UBurn ?","answer":"<p>UBurn est d\u00e9conseill\u00e9 aux femmes enceintes et allaitantes, aux enfants de moins de 18 ans, et aux personnes sous traitement m\u00e9dical sans avis pr\u00e9alable de leur m\u00e9decin. En cas de doute, consultez votre professionnel de sant\u00e9 avant de commencer.</p>","icon":"none","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"category_commande":{"type":"category","settings":{"title":"Commande et Livraison","icon":"picto-delivery","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"question_retour":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"Puis-je retourner le produit si je ne suis pas satisfait(e) ?","answer":"<p>Oui, si vous n'\u00eates pas satisfait(e) de votre achat, contactez notre service client et nous trouverons une solution adapt\u00e9e.</p>","icon":"none","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}},"question_delais_livraison":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"Quels sont les d\u00e9lais de livraison ?","answer":"<p>Nous exp\u00e9dions votre commande sous 24-48h ouvr\u00e9es. La livraison en France m\u00e9tropolitaine prend g\u00e9n\u00e9ralement 2 \u00e0 4 jours ouvr\u00e9s. La livraison est offerte d\u00e8s 30\u20ac d'achat.</p>","icon":"none","icon_width":24,"mobile_icon_width":20}}},"block_order":["category_securite","question_allergenes","question_danger_sante","category_efficacite","question_perte_poids","question_combien_temps","category_utilisation","question_quand_prendre","question_comment_preparer","category_contre_indications","question_contre_indications","category_commande","question_retour","question_delais_livraison"],"settings":{"color_scheme":"scheme-1","layout":"stacked","accordion_style":"border","question_style":"text","subheading":"QUESTIONS FR\u00c9QUENTES","title":"Tout ce que vous devez savoir sur UBurn","title_tag":"h3","content":"","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_style":"solid"}}},"order":["main","trust_icons_my9GCC","multi_column_MHejQP","ss_scrolling_logo_cloud_zHwEQq","separator_adjustable_wJXUqG","text_with_media_6nbr7X","trust_icons_jAMQBc","multi_column_QCLMjx","separator_adjustable_pQXxig","separator_adjustable_xxbed6","text_with_media_mwqBjX","text_with_media_HYdW4P","separator_adjustable_Fi6xnq","1763466816ac9eee2b","collection_list_r8VBKW","faq_ahgahg"]}